6 § 17.3. REQUISITIONS
7 (a) All purchases made under section 17.1 of this charter shall be made
8 upon written requisitions therefor upon the Purchasing Agent. The Purchasing
9 Agent shall immediately proceed to purchase under the provisions of the
10 ordinances the property so required and to distribute it accordingly taking a
11 receipt therefor upon the original requisition. The Purchasing Agent shall then
12 forward the requisition to the City Clerk. Purchases in excess of $3,000.00 the
13 amount identified in the City’s Purchasing Policy shall be awarded upon bids
14 as hereinafter set forth in this subchapter.
